window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Humor and romance mix delightfully in Katie MacAlister’s <i>New York Times</i> best-selling novels. In this installment of the Dark Ones series, Pia is discovering that wedded bliss with a vampire is a very elusive proposition. With her hubby not trusting her, and his best friend missing, Pia finds solace in her plain old Seattle life. But that all changes when she and Kristoff are falsely implicated in crimes against vampire-kind.</p>"; 
